sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant MC as scheduler
    participant CE as cmd_encoder
    participant RD as rdata_path
    participant DM as dfi_master
    participant PHY as PHY

    Note over MC,PHY: T = cycle index relative to RD command issue

    MC->>CE: cycle 0: issue RD (bank, col)
    CE->>DM: cycle 1: drive (cs_n=0, ras_n=1, cas_n=0, we_n=1)
    DM->>PHY: cycle 1: RD on dfi_address, dfi_bank

    MC->>RD: cycle 0: alert (AXI ID, burst_len)
    RD->>DM: cycle 0..CL-1: drive dfi_rddata_en=1 (anticipation)

    Note over RD: countdown CL cycles

    PHY->>DM: cycle CL: dfi_rddata_valid=1
    PHY->>DM: cycle CL: dfi_rddata (beat 1)
    PHY->>DM: cycle CL+1: dfi_rddata (beat 2)
    Note over PHY,DM: ... up to BL beats
    PHY->>DM: cycle CL+BL-1: dfi_rddata (last beat)

    DM->>RD: cycle CL: latch beats
    RD->>RD: tag beats with AXI ID

    Note over RD: stream beats to AXI R channel<br/>with rlast on final beat
